        <updateDate>2021-01-15T15:04:34Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Compassionate Care Act</b></p> <p>This bill establishes and expands various programs and activities within the Department of Health and Human Services that support and promote end-of-life care and advance care planning. It also permanently authorizes a physician or nurse practitioner to recertify via telehealth a patient's eligibility for Medicare hospice benefits.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
